Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是平常的狀態麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是平常的狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說這頂帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不好看麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮型都變的怪怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…越弄越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常不戴的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頂帽子的圖案很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖案很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的回憶還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啤酒麼 啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你喝點兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長您呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐你也喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一罐就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這桌要一罐啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個關東煮 份量好足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃個雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 你也喝點兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就喝一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 總之乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼好慶祝的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就圖個氣氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植物園大道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個樣子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:21.37,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,68)}植物園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個樣子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道才叫我來的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…來照個相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也只是入口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要照好多紀念照片的那種人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我本來以為會被拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然來了我就真的超在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是打算來約會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外你竟然這麼能出汗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要離開花店一步感覺就好起來了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋凶靈 怎麼就那麼栩栩如生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐那個東西 從空中看一遍遊樂園全景怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推薦的項目在對面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼 那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就玩這個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐點更夢幻些的東西再慢慢降溫不好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是櫻花的怨靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是內容的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道葉月君你是膽小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說我有點煩恐怖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試在入口那邊看到的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉臭屁的鴨子形便盆類似物怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫那東西天鵝船好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那是天鵝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然去玩一下剛才看到的海賊船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺涼快的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:10.72,SETTING2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz306.39\pos(586,93)}園內導遊地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚 良緣 植物園之神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 能看見天空樹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等人少了再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算高哦完全沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還沒這種東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福之橋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回頭直接走完的話就能實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你叫我了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這座橋的設定麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯉魚 你看 鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:10.59,SETTING3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(477,349)}植 物 園
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭兩次就算抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 要怎麼讓她露出那種笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算手牽手走 也完全沒有會發生什麼的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說了是約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會難道不該是興高采烈的事麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 想抽煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 現在還好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意我哦 那邊有吸煙區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用 吸煙挺浪費時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還很長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.69,setting4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(585,239)}可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就不懂就算只是一小會兒也不想分開什麼的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這…跟想像中的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是年齡的問題麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是她經常來植物園玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 煙還是先別抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不夠魄力才對 得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 我在下面看著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個去坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來幹嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被剛才的海賊船嚇到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個？好不容易來一趟的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來感受氣氛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了去吧 我在下面等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩下一個吧 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡看著就行 你們兩個去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不這麼說 我也打算把你留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的耳環 亮閃閃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作日人就少了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西 除了我們沒人坐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視野真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能…能坐你旁邊不類…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：「りんか」是日本愛知等地的方言詞尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不類？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重心會傾斜的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 不類？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這麼高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 人群就像塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：出自吉卜力動畫《天空之城》 「巴魯斯」是播放《天空之城》必念的毀滅咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會毀滅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會活得很久 這就是年紀小的好處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在介意好處什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會比店長您活得更長哦 雖然有點對不住您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青菜汁什麼的我也每天都喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很頑強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說我有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然 以後的事還是不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用現在就說的那麼確定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被異性追求的感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大年齡還是會這麼飄飄然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在許願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該在奇跡殿堂許願才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：葉月說的是bravo 店長只聽到前面兩個音就成了bra
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真理注定未來是看不透的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說店長也有可能對我傾心是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是死不放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽著手說話更能傳情達意 好像有人這麼唱過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 真是被年輕的氣魄壓倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝看開一切可是犯規的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 喜歡這雙粗糙的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞動者的手 有股向陽的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣太狡猾了 我會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不討厭吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼今天變得這麼強勢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幽靈不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣說話 是真的更容易傳情達意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟字面意思一樣 對方的心思盡在掌握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想趁他不在的時候趕緊下手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長您對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之旅 辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再坐一回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天在那裡面太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是正在美好的旅行中麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天最好是要納涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鬼屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些只會嚇人一無是處的傢伙 我可不想見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡面很涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君你要是不去的話我就自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼辦啊 我要進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我在這裡等您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您請自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您居然沒有一絲猶豫丟下我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼進來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就那樣在外面等的話也太難看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我丈夫一直是那樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉圈的太高的 太快的都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…沒必要來遊樂場吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為從美惠小姐那裡聽說了什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然說要三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這個原因麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣做是不是心眼很壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算記憶被覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不代表會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是哭哭啼啼也於事無補
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心口不一全寫您臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易結了婚 卻不得不拋下年輕的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在才開始同情幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長的眼淚掉到我心裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要什麼口味的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…對島尾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算您說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是我的驕傲自大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想過讓您選擇哪一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才 我知道葉月君你選了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是 當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主張一直都只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在打工之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這家店的次數就多到讓人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和你說話的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個會開花麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會開一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天回去的路上 我蹦了三次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也早做好準備跟那個討厭的幽靈奉陪到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體…能借給我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有生命的我能為了喜歡的人做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長…你能…和我上床麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好直截了當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…你問得這麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不可能答應啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經玩夠了麼 遊樂設施？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想玩好多種麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以隨便玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…要不要到店裡來坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開店前的流程我還沒有告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始麼 明明是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在記住比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了店長好我最應該做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才該謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊樂場之類的 如果沒有契機的話我也不會怎麼去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧 我給你泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去買包煙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在二樓 你到時候直接上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 今天真是盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可還是沒點眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沒點眉目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我身體的事呢 現在願意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 借給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你說的啊 不能反悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是個老掉牙的奇跡梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借酒消愁的人真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不用幽靈來可憐我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了 好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了在樓上等你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅子海苔茶和香料奶茶要哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別坐在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 一身酒氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛去喝酒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那傢伙喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫店長啊 總覺得有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怪唉 叫你店長什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 突然間說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝香料奶茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽到了呢 我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你個醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它脫了我去拿換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點擦一擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是活著的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:31.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも夢の中では あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:31.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中的你永遠是笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:38.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてね 消えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:38.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不會消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I care you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關心你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You care me everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你關心我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっといつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是永久的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:59.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏に降った 雪のような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:59.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正如盛夏裡飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個易碎的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我為何是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:11.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:11.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒有遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:18.69,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなに切なくて 胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:18.69,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也不會如此絞痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:22.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こともなかったそれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:22.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒能遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:35.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さも優しさも 知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:35.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就無法領悟強大與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:44.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じればすぐそこに あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:44.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼你就在離我那麼近的地方
